.TH "vmw_validation_res_reserve" 9 "vmw_validation_res_reserve" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
vmw_validation_res_reserve \- Reserve all resources registered with this validation context.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" vmw_validation_res_reserve
.BI "(struct vmw_validation_context *ctx "  ","
.BI "bool intr "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ctx" 12
The validation context.
.IP "intr" 12
Use interruptible waits when possible.
.SH "RETURN"
Zero on success, -ERESTARTSYS if interrupted. Negative error
code on failure.
